sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Trainer Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as TrainJob Controller<br/>(trainer-controller-manager)
    participant JobSetCtrl as JobSet Controller
    participant TrainPod0 as Training Pod (node-0)<br/>rank-0
    participant TrainPodN as Training Pod (node-N)
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,TrainPodN: Flow 1: TrainJob Creation and Execution

    User->>K8sAPI: POST TrainJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate TrainJob<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: API server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (allow/deny)
    K8sAPI-->>User: TrainJob created

    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event: TrainJob created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET TrainingRuntime/ClusterTrainingRuntime<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Runtime template

    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE JobSet CR<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE NetworkPolicy<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    K8sAPI->>JobSetCtrl: Watch event: JobSet created
    JobSetCtrl->>K8sAPI: CREATE Jobs/Pods<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over TrainPod0,TrainPodN: Training pods start distributed training

    TrainPod0->>TrainPodN: PyTorch rendezvous<br/>29500/TCP plaintext<br/>NetworkPolicy-restricted
    TrainPod0->>TrainPodN: NCCL collective ops<br/>all ports TCP/UDP<br/>NetworkPolicy-restricted

    Note over Controller,TrainPod0: Flow 2: Progression Tracking (RHAI)

    loop Every polling interval
        Controller->>K8sAPI: LIST pods for TrainJob<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pod list (find rank-0)
        Controller->>TrainPod0: GET /metrics<br/>28080/TCP HTTP plaintext<br/>NetworkPolicy-restricted
        TrainPod0-->>Controller: Training progress JSON<br/>(steps, epochs, ETA)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH TrainJob annotations<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    end

    Note over Prometheus,Controller: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS (insecureSkipVerify)<br/>via PodMonitor
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics
